===Etymology 2===
From {{Sp.}} ''[[vega]]'' "[[meadow]], fertile [[lowland]]" < pre-Roman [[w:Iberian language|Iberian]] '''vaica''' or '''baika''' ([[meadow]]) < Iberian '''ibai''' ([[river]]).

====Proper noun====
